Name: Space Shooter
About the game: Become the best spaceship pilot with Space Shooter which is an arcade game that can quickly wake up your hardworking side Space Shooter is an arcade game where you control a spaceship in space with a 2D view. Your objective is to survive the flyings saucers and asteroids to complete the different levels, you will see that the levels will quickly become more complex. You also have a survival mode where the difficulty gradually increases and your objective is to survive as long as possible to beat your best score and that of other players. 6 increasingly difficult levels 1 survival level playable to the controller ambient music
